dct_description_sm: Istituto Geografico de Agostini S. A. Novara ; Printed in Italy.
Longitudinal and latitudinal lines, Greenwich meridian.
List of "Sigle automobilistiche delle Provincie" = Automotive Signs of the Provinces.
Shows boundaries, principal and secondary roads, highways (including unfinished), distances between cities, state road numbers, air and sea routes, Italian and foreign customs, waterways.
Provincial coat of arm illustrations in all four margins.
Emblem of Italy at head of title appears to belong to Fascist regime (1929-1943).
